title: Psionic Comics- Rogue Science #0
description:
Publisher: Psionic Comics

Title: Rogue Science #0

Pgs.: (23 pgs. total) Cover, Inside Info, 1-20(12&13 are conjoined), Newsletter

Format: .pdf


In the great words of Dieselboy... 'A team of Rogue Scientists set a plan in motion...'


Description:

A group of scientists, bored with the scientific community, ventured off on their own.  Funded by a clandestine intelligence agency, they explored realms outside of the 'Known Universe'.  By using secret technology, they've designed a machine that allows them to travel, or port, through different universes.  They've discovered that much of our ancient history wasn't myth, and the worlds described in ancient text are found in these other universes...


So... This is the Issue #0... We had it on our site for awhile, but it took up too much traffic, so... As a gift for all... I'm releasing it to all the portal pyrates... Enjoy... And visit versethesystemstudios.com for more knowledge... We've recently finished the #0 Issue of our next title 'The Guardian Seed'... That's only available as hardcopy... But let me discuss details with the crew, and I'll see how we feel about uploading the 'Rogue Science: Ad-Lib Special Vol. 1' for you guys and femme fatales... Otherwise... Keep your third eyes peeled for some more 'Rogue Sci'...
